title: SwiftTEA: Collab Chaos Adds To Era Confusion
description:
Blondie's cinematic universe is all in on the secret and teasing us along the way.. Red TV gets a new release date, and the answer as to why is pretty obvious. Plus, Nick Jonas joins in on the fun. So many new theories and questions. TAYLOR, WHAT ARE YOU DOING TO US?
What did we miss? What theories are you buying into? Let us know! Lots of ways to contact us!
